    <string name="adaptive_how_it_works_desc">Adaptive fling uses different physics based on velocity:\n\n• Gentle swipes → precise, controlled scrolling\n• Aggressive swipes → long momentum scrolls\n\nEach mode balances these behaviors differently.</string>
    
    <!-- Adaptive Mode Descriptions -->
    <string name="adaptive_balanced">Balanced: Controlled for gentle swipes, more momentum for aggressive swipes. Best for general use.</string>
    <string name="adaptive_precision">Precision: Prioritizes control. Even aggressive swipes stop quickly. Best for text-heavy content.</string>
    <string name="adaptive_momentum">Momentum: Prioritizes distance. Swipes travel farther. Best for galleries and feeds.</string>
    
